Name: Hasty Conscription
Cost: 2
Effect: Place a pawn from your reserves anywhere on your first 3 ranks.

Name: New Recruits
Cost: 5
Effect: Place a pawn or minor piece from your reserves anywhere on your first 3 ranks.

Name: Skirmisher Lines*
Cost: 2
Effect: Pawns on your second rank can advance up to 3 spaces.

Name: Clearance Sacrifice
Cost: 3
Effect: Sacrifice a pawn. Add a pawn to your reserves.